How about...never give anyone anything w/o something in return.

It's ridiculously stupid to give someone any coin and press trade w/o anything being on his side of the trade window.

It would be impossible to rip you off in a casino type scam, if you put the money up in the window but didn't hit trade.  Then random, if you lose press trade, if you win wait for him to put your winnings up plus whatever you have up (or just cancel and have him give you the winnings).

If they won't do that, then they are a scammer.

